ActEconomic Action Plan 2013 Act, No. 2
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on Which this Order is Made as the Day on Which Sections 263, 266 and 267 of the Economic Action Plan 2013 Act, No. 2 Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which this order is made as the day on which sections 263, 266 and 267 of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2013 ACT, NO. 2, chapter 40 of the Statutes of Canada, 2013, COME INTO FORCE in order to (1) repeal the two obsolete Acts of Parliament; and (2) remove five obsolete references from the Schedule to the International Bridges and Tunnels Act.
